               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420822-name-419" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-419" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-419" type="surname" value="LOVELL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-419" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LOVELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am foreman to William Roberts, of Wigmore-street. In consequence of information, on the 8th of July, I ran into Harley-street, and saw the prisoner with a saddle on his arm—I cried "Stop thief"—he ran with the saddle, and threw it on a wagon—this is it, it is my master's—after a long race I succeeded in taking him.</p>
