                  </hi>. I was in Wigmore-street—I saw the prisoner run<lb></lb>ning up the street with a saddle—I took it up, and took it back to Mr. Roberts's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was out of work, and in great distress; it was a great temptation.</p>
